                            <comment id="217608" author="jay" created="Fri, 5 Jan 2018 18:19:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Andreas - this is about the policy for picking a replica for write. FLR is still useful for read w/o this feature.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
